<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.3.10">
<l>tēṉamar cōlai nāṅkainaṉ ṉaṭuvuḷ cempoṉcey kōyili ṉuḷḷē</l>
<l>vāṉavar kōṉaik kaṇṭamai collum maṅkaiyār vāṭkali kaṉṟi</l>
<l>yūṉamil pāṭa loṉpatō ṭoṉṟu moḻiviṉṟik kaṟṟuval lārkaḷ</l>
<l>māṉaveṇ kuṭaikkīḻ vaiyaka māṇṭu vāṉava rākuvar makiḻntē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master learning the nine-and-one faultless songs,</l>
<l rend="indent">without omissions,</l>
<l>Of sword[-bearing] Kalikaṉṟi of those of Maṅkai,</l>
<l rend="indent">who speaks of seeing the celestials’ king</l>
<l>Within the Cempoṉcey Temple right in the center of Nāṅkai,</l>
<l rend="indent">with groves where honey is plentiful,</l>
<l>Having ruled the world under a proud, white parasol,</l>
<l rend="indent">they will joyfully become celestials.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
